Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

I understand that a prior spec and the implementation thereof removed the ability for this but I think the options should take advantage of oslo.config 1.9.0 and use deprecated_for_removal=True. Note: you'll need to rebase on-top of the current openstack proposal bot change to requirements.txt.

In other words, I think the options should stick around even if they're non-operative/do-nothing options. Thanks Chris
